{"tid":453472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[雖遠必誅]5月被ISIS 綁架的兩名中國人已經被殺","createTime":"2017-10-31T08:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T10:52:16.000Z","uid":47352,"like":191,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"138b41ec2433c79d337cb4d71c52b474d9b85912","tid":453472,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦外交部30日發出聲明，確認今年5月被ISIS 綁架的兩名中國人已經死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今年5月24日，3名中國人在巴基斯坦俾路支省（Balochistan）首府奎達市（Quetta）一家餐廳吃午餐時，遭遇3名持槍的假警察綁架。其中一男一女被強行帶走，之後失蹤，而另一名同行女子逃脫。<br />\n<br />\n被綁架的一男一女分別為李欣恒（Li Xinheng，音譯）與孟麗斯（Meng Lisi，音譯）。二人一度誤傳為夫婦，後被澄清為好友關係，在一間由韓國人開設的語言機構教中文。"},{"pid":"1824b87e964edc48a68b463c97fefdfa9890a6c2","tid":453472,"uid":119494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb929e5a33298da3a8c9b0e15cf215ff58cf9b7f","tid":453472,"uid":38671,"like":264,"dislike":2,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.bkcimg.com/uploads/image/201707/27/1501189505560085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.bkcimg.com%2Fuploads%2Fimage%2F201707%2F27%2F1501189505560085.jpg&h=da34155d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5fc16e85b38c154fe5cbfb7a56ecd3eddea7b65","tid":453472,"uid":23635,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"吳京仲唔出動？"},{"pid":"71a890b900889450b8283d9f5a68d2b9a5586713","tid":453472,"uid":22858,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛在何方</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字試用版</ins><br />\n<br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<br />\n